{"TopicId":201805,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"One button Navball resizing","CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-18T12:35:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-18T12:35:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi to all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like to play with the nav ball off to the left and about 60% size to save on the screen real-estate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut that makes the ball a bit hard to read when trying for a tight manoeuvre while flying manually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, as the title says can we have a button to go from one size to another on the fly?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the read.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-18T17:31:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d be happy with a simple texture upgrade so the navball remains more readable at smaller sizes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBarring that, a way to toggle between default and custom size would be welcome indeed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-18T20:08:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be good too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbout the sizes I would like to go custom size to another custom size.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSay 60% to 200% and back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ben J. Kerman","CreatedById":204948,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-19T15:12:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223956635\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618749339\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158362\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Martian Emigrant\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/18/2021 at 8:35 AM, Martian Emigrant said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnav ball off to the left and about 60% size to save on the screen real-estate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t even know you could change the size at all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T02:01:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223957145\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618845124\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204948\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ben J. Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Ben J. Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t even know you could change the size at all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204948-ben-j-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204948\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204948-ben-j-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ben J. Kerman\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I am running linux, from the game its escape, setting, scroll down the list.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022yobO6cL.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002298.00\u0022 height=\u0022735\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yobO6cL.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can resize pretty much any info along the sides of the screen frame.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nM E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-23T20:11:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022158362\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Martian Emigrant\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0 I get what you mean, I suggested the same thing not too long ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou want it smaller for \u0027normal\u0027 use, but then\u00A0you want it larger to help with more \u0027delicate\u0027 tasks.\u00A0 The little \u0027hide\u0027 tab is great, but it does what it says and hides it (as it should).\u00A0 \u00A0Whereas an extra toggle\u00A0to switch between two custom sizes would allow that functionality too.\u00A0 Or perhaps use the existing \u0027hide\u0027 tab to cycle through the three options to avoid an extra button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-23T21:19:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223959721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619208663\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130621\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pandaman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n51 minutes ago, pandaman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022158362\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Martian Emigrant\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0 I get what you mean, I suggested the same thing not too long ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou want it smaller for \u0027normal\u0027 use, but then\u00A0you want it larger to help with more \u0027delicate\u0027 tasks.\u00A0 The little \u0027hide\u0027 tab is great, but it does what it says and hides it (as it should).\u00A0 \u00A0Whereas an extra toggle\u00A0to switch between two custom sizes would allow that functionality too.\u00A0 Or perhaps use the existing \u0027hide\u0027 tab to cycle through the three options to avoid an extra button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/130621-pandaman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022130621\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/130621-pandaman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@pandaman\u003C/a\u003E I totally forgot about the hide function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn every install I disable it so the Navball is always present. I always refer to\u00A0 it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like your idea of toggling between\u00A0 3 different states. But it is not for us to choose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe shall see what the creators in charge will do with this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow is the spring in the UK? I haven\u0027t been across the pond to your side of it (The pond that is) in over 12-13 years. I enjoyed every stay. As short as they were.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere in Montr\u00E9al we had a very nice early one but we just had 2 days of cold with snow.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSoon motorcycles and vegetable gardens. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-24T09:07:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223959756\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619212775\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158362\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Martian Emigrant\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Martian Emigrant said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like your idea of toggling between\u00A0 3 different states. But it is not for us to choose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, not our choice, but that\u0027s what the suggestions section\u00A0is for.\u00A0 If the devs think it worthwhile then it could get included.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022158362\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158362-martian-emigrant/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Martian Emigrant\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0 Will PM you shortly in response to the rest so as not to go off topic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T19:29:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m in the process of making this idea into a new mini-mod. You can grab the beta version here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022210116\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1657929819\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/202040-wip-navball-size-toggler/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:191px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently, you double tap the \u0022navball hide\u0022 shortcut on the keyboard (Keypad Del/. on mine) to switch sizes but I plan to implement a button as suggested.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}